  <contentSectionDescription><![CDATA[<p>We are truly passionate about delivering great value ski holidays to our customers, as well as premium <a data-udi="umb://document/13cca02f7ef4467cade8c8e89e68fe39" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13cca02f7ef4467cade8c8e89e68fe39}" title="Snowboarding Holidays">snowboarding</a> packages. No matter if it’s enjoying luxury <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austrian ski resorts</a>, to some of the top destinations such as <a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" title="St Anton">St Anton</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" title="Zell am See">Zell am See</a>, a <a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays">group ski holiday</a> in France to stunning resorts including <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606}" title="Montgenèvre">Montgenevre</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4}" title="La Plagne">La Plagne</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540" href="/{localLink:umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540}" title="Avoriaz">Avoriaz</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Meribel</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>, a beautiful mountain hotel in Italy in some of the most iconic places like <a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89}" title="Livigno">Livigno</a> and the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites</a> ski area, a dream trip to Canada in <a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff">Banff</a>, or a <a data-udi="umb://document/d137b11ca7414c7b817405b2fd7405b8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d137b11ca7414c7b817405b2fd7405b8}" title="Ski Weekends &amp; Short Breaks to Switzerland">short break</a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Moritz</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa4963